# AI Student Grading System

##  Project Description
This project is a Python-based system that calculates student marks, average, and grade using conditional logic.

##  Features
- Calculates total marks
- Computes average score
- Assigns grade based on performance
- Simple and easy-to-understand logic

##  Technologies Used
- Python
- Jupyter Notebook

##  Project File
- student-grading-system.ipynb

## 📈 Future Improvements
- Add graphical user interface (GUI)
- Store student data in a database
- Apply machine learning for grade prediction

